UPHENDUKE iqhawe umshayeli wetekisi ebelethisa umgibeli wesifazane obexinwe ukusikwa. UMnuz Nhlonipho Zulu (31) ongumshayeli wetekisi ebelisuka kwaNongoma liya eRichards Bay uthi ubengakaze azicabange ebelethisa umuntu wesifazane empilweni yakhe kodwa ugcine esephoqeleka ukubhekana ngqo nalesi simo emuva kokuthi umgibeli obesesele yedwa eteskisini exinwe ukusikwa sebesele bobabili. Thola udaba oluphelele kwiSolezwe lakusasa nalaphoÂ  lo mshayeli nowesifazane obelethisiwe begeqa amagula ngalesi sehlo. 